* Do not keep any secrets,credentails,username in your pipeline or project files.
* With gitlab you can define envinormet variables that will be avaliable running the pipeline.
* Envinorment variables are ideal for storing secrets when working with gitlab CI. 


# Surge token --- In gitbash
* copy the token and paste in the gitlab
* In gitbal > select > select project > In project rightside we have settings > select CICD > Select Variables > add variable. 